Author: hollowberry_
Text: Some stuff don't come up easily. As a harm reduction approach, if I'm panicking and doing a lot of damage with no results, I flood the situation with club soda. The bubbles bust up the food inside. Then I try again. Cuz f\*#& knows I'm going to keep going until I get the result, and I need to somehow reduce the damage I'm causing, until someday I can stop the behaviour. :/ owie the throat. I hope you're okay :(
